
== SWT dialogs
	<indexterm>
		<primary>Dialog</primary>
		<secondary>SWT</secondary>
	</indexterm>
	
		SWT provides an API to use the native dialogs from the OS
		platform.
		The
		default SWT
		dialogs are listed below.

		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				
					`ColorDialog`
					- for selecting a color
				
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				
					`DirectoryDialog`
					- for selecting a directory
				
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				
					`FileDialog`
					- for selecting a file
				
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				
					`FontDialog`
					- for selecting a font
				
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				
					`MessageBox`
					- for opening a message dialog
				
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	
	
